Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:31.95,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\bord2\fad(10,10)\pos(516,269)\3c&HE954E9&}真唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:32.70,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 最后一招下得真有气势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:33.65,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:34.41,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(10,250)\bord2\pos(249,380)\3c&HDC0000&}优希对了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:37.75,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这样就可以把这些子都提走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.75,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\3c&HDC0000&\bord2\pos(200,422)}这招就叫做{\3c&H2221EE&}「困鹤巢」!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:39.54,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这次该怎么下呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:40.17,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:43.13,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\bord2\fad(10,10)\pos(295,382)\3c&HEB49EB&}这次由真唯来挑战!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:44.05,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\3c&H2221EE&\bord2\an7\pos(380,343)\fad(350,134)}当左右棋形一样时\N多数情况下中间的地方就是急所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:48.17,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:50.93,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以很顺利地救出白子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.36,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在实际对局中运用这些手筋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:55.16,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下围棋就会变得越来越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:55.02,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\bord2\3c&H0A670F&\pos(318,383)\fad(10,354)}运用好手筋的话 下围棋就会变得越来越有趣了哦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.35,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H0000FF&\pos(494,388)}{\bord2}{\fad(230,0)}待续…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【下回预告】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想来个团体赛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团体赛?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手如果是围棋会场的大叔们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让三子也要打败他们才行
